    ],
    "The book sparked the so-called \u201cVera debate\u201d, prompting a number of counter-publications, and was considered scandalous within the women\u2019s movement.": [],
    "In 1903, she married Peter Paul Kurth (1879\u20131924), a lawyer and archaeologist.": [
