    "Her dissertation was titled <em>Die Fresken im Adlerturm zu Trient</em> (<em>The Frescoes in the Eagle Tower in Trento</em>), and was published under the title \u201cEin Freskenzyklus im Adlerturm zu Trient\u201d (\u201cA Cycle of Frescoes in the Eagle Tower at Trento\u201d) in the <em>Jahrbuch des Kunsthistorischen Institutes</em> in Vienna in 1911.": [],
