    "Her papers on Gothic painting and iconography were significant in studies of medieval art history, and her volumes concerning German medieval tapestries became \u201cindispensable to all students of the subject\u201d and \u201ca model of conscientious and successful research into technique, style, history and above all iconography\u201d.": [],
